Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,VAV STUDIO .:. VIETTORRENT.VN\Nwww.facebook.com/VAV.AudioViet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,VAV STUDIO\N© Copyright 2013, All rights reserved
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Episode 19{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was here not too long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably trying\Nto get back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jung Yoo Gun, Ji Soo Yun\Nand Kim Yun Hwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Woo must be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the reason Yoon Shi Hyuk\Nis doing this to Hyun Woo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,While trying to escape, Yoon Shi Hyuk\Ngot shot by Hyun Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Woo thinks Shi Hyuk is\Ntrying to get back at him for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on...\Nwith Kim Yun Hwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been helping me\Nto capture Yoo Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you trust her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If she isn't with me...\Nshe has nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,About that hard drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can retrieve the information inside\Nthere only through the NSS's main server.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about asking for\Nsuch a difficult thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You really aren't going\Nto come back to the NSS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently on the wanted list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me until...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I catch Yoo Joong Won, Soo Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I'll turn myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not to the hospital.\NTake me back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- But...\N- Just listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.\NI'll see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't they fix\Nthe broken surveillance camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo Joong Won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggested you the way of patriots\Nbecause I've got extra time on my hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd made myself clear that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll be okay after...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Black is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I eliminated the Director\Nof NSS Kang Chul Hwan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You did an unnecessary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier today, Deputy Director\NChoi Min tried to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,hand over the nuclear weapons\Nto the U.S..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kang Chul Hwan and Ji Soo Yun\Napparently stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kang Chul Hwan isn't an obstacle\Nto our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use him well,\Nhe could be a great help to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kang Chul Hwan refused\Nour offer to join us and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he's been dying to capture us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more than just a few trying to\Ncapture our hidden IRIS operatives out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't eliminate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is to use them without letting\Nthem realize that they are being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you act alone again\Nwithout my permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll be the end of\Nour relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The President must be really pressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He informed me of further details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They secured four nuclear warheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Baek San still has the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to meet with\NBaek San tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I want you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you were very agitated,\Nso I've held it on to it until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If not now, I didn't think I'd\Nhave the chance to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Joong Won.\NIt must be so tough for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whether you're not skipping any meals,\Nor where you've been sleeping...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lose sleep at night thinking\Nand worrying about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This morning, people from\Nthe security command came by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:12:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They turned your room upside down\Nsearching for something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I asked what it was about but they\Njust got angry and didn't tell me anything. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The people are saying something\Nbad must have happened to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just hope that it's nothing serious. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so sorry that your mother\Ncan't be of any help to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure if it's the right thing do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to tell you this when you've\Ngot so much on your plate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My health has deteriorated\Na lot lately so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't help thinking that\NI may not be able to see you again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to see you\Nget married before I die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Joong Won, even if I don't get\Nto see you again, don't be too sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We all have to die at some point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've saved all the money\Nyou sent me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would an old woman like me\Nneed to spend all this money on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Behind the house, under the big jar...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I kept all the money there inside\Na plastic bag so that it wouldn't get wet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That should be able to get you a wardrobe\Nand several beddings when you get married.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I was going to give you the jade ring\Nyour father gave me to your bride.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just in case,\NI want you to hold on to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I trust that everything will\Nturn out fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And don't even think about\Navenging your brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:14:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think of it as Heaven's will.\NPlease be well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish for your happiness.\NLove, your mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to look inside\Nthe hard drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm not in a situation where\NI can get help from the NSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you see the information\Nin the hard drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be even more disappointed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All the things I've done are\Nstored inside that hard drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yoo Gun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I couldn't leave\Nyou any good memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,like most fathers leave for\Ntheir children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't get involved in\Nthis any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, just return to your normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to Soo Yun and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,lead an ordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo Gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I really... really am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's late but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly thankful that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to know you finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are... all these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how worried I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You were suffering all night.\NBut I had no idea what was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try taking something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all the non-prescription\Nextra strength painkillers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a broken rib,\Nbut I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You were very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you know Yoo Joong Won\Nwould be after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't normally wear\Na bullet proof vest and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some time ago, he tried to persuade me\Nto join him. Of course, I refused him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he would try to\Nretaliate in some shape or form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:18:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, I was very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi, how are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Anthony Choi from the\NJeron Research Group.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was put in charge of this research\Nby the President of South Korea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to secure and transfer\Nthe original nuclear technology... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the research teams from Jeron and\Nthe Agency from Defense Development{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be collaborating\Nuntil the end of this project.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the President's order to move\None of the nuclear weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a request from Jeron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the President is rushing things because\Nof the incident with Deputy Director Choi Min.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's about 13 kilometers until\Nwe get to the target location.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay. Be on standby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the nuclear weapons\Nis getting moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried because you\Nweren't answering your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, I'm fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do have something I\Nneed to confirm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of the nuclear weapons is getting moved\Nfrom the Agency for Defense Development.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you know anything about this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard it from the director\Na short while ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the Pentagon finds out about\Nthe nuclear warheads through Choi Min...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,some measures will be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're going to separate all four\Nwarheads to carry out the research.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you find out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For safety purpose, the Deputy Director\Nhas put a tracking device on each warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where are they going to carry out\Nthe research after they've been separated?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the President consulted\Nan armament manufacturer called Jeron.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An armament manufacturer called Jeron?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Anthony Choi, a Korean-American, is\Ncurrently the CEO of the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the status with the hard drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to access\Nthe main server room, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I have the info,\NI'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anthony Choi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be carrying out a\Nsecurity inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo Gun was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you, Yoo Jong Chul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son makes me want\Nto recruit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as much as when you were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.59,0:24:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret killing all those nuclear scientists\Nnot even knowing who they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame that I couldn't kill you,\Nthe one I really should have killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have realized what kind of person\Nyou are and come back to my senses sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the Baek San\NI know is regretting now, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.63,0:24:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a regret...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but if something was done wrong,\NI feel like I should make it right again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop doing this thing you are doing\Nwith the Hawk faction in the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.42,0:24:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My plan is very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.07,0:24:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This country has been in\Na state of truce for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ironically, the ones who are\Nliving in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.83,0:24:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have become immune\Nto the fear of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.24,0:24:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.74,0:25:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to end the ongoing war.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.36,0:25:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.24,0:25:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This country is currently\Nin the state of truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.37,0:25:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still technically in a war\Nthat has yet to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.36,0:25:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we get to the point now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.89,0:25:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over Yoo Joong Won to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.78,0:25:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll hand over the last\Nnuclear weapon to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.47,0:25:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that you'd be so easy\Nand not put up a fight at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.33,0:25:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance,\Nis it because of your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have Yoo Joong Won\Nanytime after I'm finished with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.53,0:25:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm skeptical that you'd actually\Nhand over the nuclear weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.59,0:25:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no other objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.28,0:25:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The exchange between Yoo Joong Won\Nand the nuclear weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.81,0:25:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.21,0:26:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in touch again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.18,0:26:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being tailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.86,0:26:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.63,0:26:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.24,0:27:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me stay with you\Nuntil the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.44,0:27:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you've done a lot of work.\NThank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.65,0:27:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your help,\NI couldn't come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.22,0:27:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.44,0:27:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Find Matsumoto and he'll help\Nyou get settled in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.42,0:27:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Director.\N- Do as I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.66,0:27:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And do not tell Yoo Gun\Nabout my movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.53,0:28:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've transferred all the files from\Nthe hard drive into here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.75,0:28:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.87,0:28:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything else you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.16,0:28:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning...\NI got a call from Baek San.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.40,0:28:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like he was planning\Non doing something today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.46,0:28:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you... let him hear you\Ncall him 'father'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.63,0:29:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jung Yoo Gun,\Nthis is Jang Chul.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.21,0:29:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's been assisting\NDirector Baek San.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.18,0:29:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.38,0:29:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.73,0:29:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Director told me not\Nto tell you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.09,0:29:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought you should know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.09,0:29:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the ADD and find out\Nwhether there are any survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.29,0:29:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.17,0:29:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The nuclear weapon has gone\Nmissing during the transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.29,0:29:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.88,0:29:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Team Leader Yoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.39,0:29:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's at the Agency\Nfor Defense Development (ADD).
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.46,0:29:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.04,0:29:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The nuclear weapon transport team\Ncame under an attack and went missing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.67,0:29:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,during the transport from the ADD\Nto the Jeron research center.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.82,0:29:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How many casualties?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.08,0:29:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone from the Jeron research\Nteam and all of the soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.22,0:30:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They look too much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.36,0:30:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me here.\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.25,0:30:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Director made me\Npromise not to tell you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.03,0:31:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you should know\Nabout it since you are his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.35,0:31:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.20,0:31:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Director went to go meet Mr. Black, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.71,0:31:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him I would escort him but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.38,0:31:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's trying to lure Mr. Black in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.86,0:31:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lure him in? To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.29,0:31:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he'll be going to the place\Nwhere he's hidden his nuclear weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.32,0:31:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.18,0:31:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Soo Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.20,0:32:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo Gun, do you still have the tracing\Ndevice for the nuclear weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.13,0:32:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.46,0:32:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the nuclear weapons\Nhas gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.81,0:32:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And Anthony Choi is making a strong\Nprotest against the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.43,0:32:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Soo Yun. Listen to me carefully, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.69,0:32:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anthony Choi's real name\Nis Yoo Jong Chul and....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.77,0:32:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he is the nuclear scientist that disappeared\Nduring the 4th administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.71,0:32:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Mr. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.59,0:32:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anthony Choi is... Mr. Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.64,0:32:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to the information\NI got from the National Archives...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.74,0:32:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In 1979, after President Park's death...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.52,0:32:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Director Kim Jung Yong from the\NCentral Intelligence Service and the CIA...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.89,0:32:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}made a hit list consisting\Nof five people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.38,0:32:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the time, Baek San killed three on the list\Nwithout even knowing who they were.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.65,0:32:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In 2009, scientist Yoo Jong Won\Nwas killed by Baek San again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.42,0:32:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, the one who ordered the killing was\NYoo Jong Won's brother Yoo Jong Chul.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.19,0:32:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Yoo Jong Chul is Mr. Black.\NIn other words, he's Anthony Choi, now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.25,0:32:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the five nuclear scientists,\Nthe one who survived was Mr. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.27,0:33:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the information you sent me,\NI confirmed that they are the same person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.69,0:33:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the one who hijacked\Nthe nuclear weapon was Yoo Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.80,0:33:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Anthony Choi is behind that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.65,0:33:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the nuclear weapon\Nthat's been hijacked, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.07,0:33:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If they've discovered the tracing device,\Nthe current location could be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.75,0:33:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find out first and call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.61,0:33:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anthony Choi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.96,0:33:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Black of IRIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.70,0:33:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.50,0:33:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We suspect that Yoo Jong Chul,\Nwho's disguised as Anthony Choi
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.73,0:33:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,has planned this whole thing with\NYoo Joong Won from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.61,0:33:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our current utmost priority is to locate\NAnthony Choi and Yoo Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.90,0:33:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That means... I arranged to have\Nour President and IRIS meet
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.15,0:33:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and basically handed over\Nthe nuclear weapons to Mr. Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.09,0:34:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ji Soo Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.04,0:34:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in touch with Jung Yoo Gun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.15,0:34:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No use denying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.85,0:34:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I already got his contact number\Nfrom the Deputy Director's cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.49,0:34:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've asked him help locate\Nthe missing nuclear weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.91,0:34:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Leader Jung has the tracer that\Ncould locate the nuclear weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.24,0:34:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can contact Jung Yoo Gun to find out\Nthe location of the missing nuclear weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.06,0:34:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, Team Leader Jung is in\Nthe process of confirming the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.42,0:34:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll continue to be in\Ncommunication with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.09,0:34:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the time the\Nnuclear weapon has gone missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.42,0:34:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we've been tracing its movement through\Nthe CCTVs in the surrounding areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.88,0:34:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, our utmost priority is\Nthe recovery of the missing nuclear weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.15,0:34:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel all other missions in progress\Nand focus on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.77,0:34:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Jung Yoo Gun and\Nmake him join the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.48,0:34:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to have him\Npardoned and...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.52,0:35:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,until we are 100 percent sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.87,0:35:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll keep Anthony Choi's identity\Nas classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.53,0:37:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Put down the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.29,0:37:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to die together,\Nyou can tell me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.62,0:37:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep quiet and follow me,\NI can show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.83,0:37:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift up the rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.44,0:38:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Report it to Mr. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.66,0:38:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.04,0:38:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed... the nuclear weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.71,0:38:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's holding a remote control\Ndevice with a switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.61,0:38:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Baek San there?\NLet me talk to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.53,0:38:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You did an unnecessary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.23,0:38:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do need a confirmation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.46,0:38:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hand over Yoo Joong Won,\Nour deal will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.40,0:38:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the remote control\Ndevice you are holding?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.84,0:38:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You wouldn't be thinking about\Na suicide bombing, would you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.49,0:38:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only weapon I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.91,0:38:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your safety house is within\Na 10 kilometer radius from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.74,0:39:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are thinking about playing\Ntricks, give it up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.77,0:39:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll also disappear with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.88,0:39:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You already know where I am.\NYou're indeed Baek San.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.63,0:39:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, is our deal on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.26,0:39:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on over to me.\NI'll hand over Yoo Joong Won.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.35,0:39:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the device working now?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.72,0:39:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It is and I'm getting close\Nbut it's little complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.69,0:39:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the EOD team\Nwatch all the major highways.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.84,0:39:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.45,0:39:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnify the front passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.02,0:39:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.59,0:39:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Park Tae Hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.00,0:39:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Park Tae Hee?\N- She's in disguise but I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.79,0:39:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.17,0:40:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.59,0:40:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When's the D-day?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.23,0:40:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.78,0:40:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to hurry up and prepare a\Ndetonator for this bomb as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.16,0:40:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How should we prepare it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.82,0:40:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the plan,\Nprepare it two different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.79,0:40:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.12,0:41:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least once...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.58,0:41:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I wanted to call you\Nas my heart desired, Yoo Gun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.40,0:41:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My son... Yoo Gun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.03,0:41:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moment I saw you\Nfor the first time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.91,0:41:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my desire to live became stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.18,0:41:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really have... ended so many\Nlives with my own hands. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.83,0:41:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now that, I'm thinking about paying\Nfor the crimes I've committed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.84,0:41:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's not that easy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.66,0:41:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moment I found out that\Nyou and your mother were alive...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.38,0:41:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the first time in 30 years...\NI wanted to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.73,0:41:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the opportunity arises...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.06,0:42:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd like to meet you again\Nas a father and a son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.69,0:42:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to become a good\Nfather to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.56,0:42:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.48,0:42:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.03,0:43:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the nuclear weapon\NBaek San has?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.63,0:43:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've confirmed the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.66,0:43:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.01,0:43:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.86,0:43:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.41,0:43:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Black's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.01,0:44:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.88,0:44:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How many operatives are there\Nwhom I can trust to be on my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.57,0:44:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than the seven including\NHyuk Soo and Chul Min...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.30,0:44:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone else is part of\NYoon Shi Hyuk's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.89,0:44:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.18,0:44:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... after Mr. Black has secured\NBaek San's nuclear weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.43,0:44:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,he might try to corner me with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.79,0:44:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's underestimated\NYoo Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.72,0:44:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a good\Nfeeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.11,0:44:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to have a plan just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.26,0:44:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.27,0:44:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.03,0:44:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.38,0:45:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find where\NBaek San is first.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.56,0:45:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split up to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.62,0:45:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever finds him first\Nwill call the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.46,0:45:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.14,0:45:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mr. Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.22,0:45:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.37,0:46:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.96,0:46:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.13,0:46:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Yoo Joong Won?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.34,0:46:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the first room on the right\Non the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.55,0:48:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to use the nuclear weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.21,0:48:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you should use it for something\Nmore productive.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.12,0:48:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To catch a small fry like me,\Nyou want to drain the whole pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.36,0:48:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need for self-deprecation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.85,0:48:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gone, that will pose a\Nbig problem to IRIS's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.56,0:48:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if your nuclear bomb goes off,\Nit'll have no effect on the IRIS headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.71,0:48:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know that better\Nthan anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.83,0:48:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.24,0:48:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've said before,\NI've secured one already.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.02,0:48:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The South Korean government\Nhas handed it over to me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.66,0:48:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Their greed to possess nuclear\Nweapons and...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.16,0:48:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,their excessively cautious attitude\Nto keep things secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.00,0:48:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,has placed the nuclear weapon\Ninto my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.17,0:48:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.91,0:49:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.82,0:49:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.91,0:49:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hand over Yoo Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.75,0:49:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So hand that device over to me, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.17,0:49:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yun Hwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.16,0:49:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.98,0:49:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand and just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.60,0:49:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.81,0:49:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to stop you\Nfrom getting killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.55,0:49:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to your senses and\Nsay something that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.54,0:49:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been helping Jung Yoo Gun\Nwho's been after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.36,0:49:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you say\Nyou're worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.47,0:50:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to stop me\Nfrom getting killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.06,0:50:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.27,0:50:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you could say while aiming\Na gun to my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.73,0:50:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking a lot about how\Nto end the fight that one has to die for.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.58,0:50:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is only one conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.03,0:50:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.23,0:50:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop what you are trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.43,0:50:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping IRIS to instigate a war...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.52,0:50:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can just stop that,\NI can convince Jung Yoo Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.74,0:50:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.88,0:50:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know very well why\NJung Yoo Gun is trying to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.89,0:50:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.38,0:50:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,killed Jung Yoo Gun's mother, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.99,0:50:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it from his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.78,0:50:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You love your mother more\Nthan anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.73,0:51:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what made me\Nhold a gun at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.95,0:51:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother who suffered a miserable death.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.06,0:51:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister whom I don't even\Nknow is dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.28,0:51:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I came this far to avenge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.93,0:51:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I even ended up\Npointing a gun at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.40,0:51:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I swore all the hardliners\Nfrom the Republic are my enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.04,0:51:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,even you became my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.69,0:51:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to become\Nmy enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.41,0:51:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.69,0:51:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said before, let's just go some\Nplace where no one will find us...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.37,0:51:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and just live there in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.48,0:51:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in this country where you can't\Nsurvive unless you step on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.43,0:52:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find a place where there\Nis no greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.55,0:52:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go live there, Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.07,0:52:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the Director is in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.16,0:52:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.62,0:53:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.70,0:53:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find Baek San first.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.34,0:53:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry before they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.18,0:55:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, Baek San's location\Nhas been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.57,0:55:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be right there. Gather the\Noperatives and locate the intruders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.44,0:55:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.45,0:55:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.71,0:55:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You were tailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.98,0:56:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.25,0:56:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Leader Jung.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.75,0:57:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to fight you\Nat some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.90,0:57:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.65,0:58:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.44,0:58:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- What the hell are you...\N- Your father is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.86,0:58:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you wish to see your father, come to the\Nbasement under the center staircase. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.40,0:58:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.37,0:58:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over that remote control\Nand leave here with your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.08,0:58:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.60,0:59:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try convincing\Nyour father?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.26,0:59:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Many innocent people are about\Nto evaporate from a nuclear bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.36,0:59:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.35,0:59:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no end to\Na revenge such as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.37,0:59:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like... this to be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.72,0:59:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo Joong Won is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.69,0:59:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand that over to me and\Ntake Yoo Joong Won with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.92,0:59:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, your excessive greed\Nto possess nuclear weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.72,1:00:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,has blurred your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.12,1:00:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said this remote control...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.16,1:00:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is to detonate the nuclear bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.89,1:00:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.23,1:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think my target\Nwas Yoo Joong Won?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.72,1:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Baek San.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.15,1:00:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.64,1:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Yoo Gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.62,1:01:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.67,1:01:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.17,1:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.22,1:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by DramaFever
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.36,1:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared.\NYoo Joong Won took it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.15,1:02:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared for this?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.65,1:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,His goal is to detonate the\Nnuclear bomb to start a war.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.64,1:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Find it no matter what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.53,1:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need Team Leader Jung's help\Nin finding the weapon, get him involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.08,1:03:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to end this psychological\Nwarfare that always ends with threats?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.27,1:03:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 1.2 million liberation soldiers\Nof the Republic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.36,1:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. If you succeed...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.50,1:03:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll all become the heroes of\Nthe Democratic People's Republic of Korea.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.52,1:03:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely going to make it successful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.50,1:03:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, the NSS and the police\Nwill surround the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.82,1:03:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt,\NJung Yoo Gun will be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.19,1:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be great as a buddy to accompany\Non my way to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.25,1:03:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the representative of the people?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.59,1:03:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't delude yourself, Yoo Joong Won.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.16,1:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's only your pent-up anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.92,1:03:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Joong Won.\N- Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.18,1:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not die.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.31,1:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's hard, let's live.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.32,1:03:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start this holy war for\Nthe unification.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.20,1:03:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,VAV STUDIO .:. VIETTORRENT.VN\Nwww.facebook.com/VAV.AudioViet\N© Copyright 2013, All rights reserved